OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening though a few late sunny
OL,7,Fintervals in the north. Some patches
OL,8,Fof rain over Southern Aberdeenshire,
OL,9,Fthese becoming more widespread
OL,10,Fovernight with the odd heavier
OL,11,Foutbreak.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy rain in the morning
OL,15,Fbecoming more patchy in the afternoon
OL,16,Fwith some drier brighter spells. Quite
OL,17,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
